name: JamJockey
tag_list: iphone, music, streaming, songs, playlists, free
overview:
Simple, free, streaming music on your iPhone!

JamJockey (www.jamjockey.com) is a simple web application that allows you to search for millions of songs and stream them to your iPhone, right from the Safari web browser. No app download required! Just simple, free, unlimited streaming of any song you want to hear.

JamJockey looks and feels like a native iPhone app. Moreover, audio playback is fully integrated with the iPhone’s native controls, so you can listen while multi-tasking and control playback with your headphones!

Along with instant streaming, the app also incorporates album coverart for a nice look, and has a functioning playlist and favorites list so it’s actually useful!

No signup required, all playlist data is stored locally in your browser.

Visit jamjockey.com on your iPhone or iPod Touch!
